{"tid":1373300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時到我地見狗就打？","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:19:11.000Z","uid":224836,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b56938f71b9662a3bbeceaf7a97bdafca8a25d3e","tid":1373300,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"發夢鄉黑警狗兩邊都已經開無雙亂棍打人 幾時到我地見狗就打呀？<br />\n比人恰到上心口啦你老母<br />\n仲忍？<br />\n呢一個星期有幾多無辜市民都受傷呀<br />\n無裝備既普通大叔都比人打到咁<br />\n仲要忍？ <br />\n之前發夢話玩魔法果堆 要勇武果堆 今日去哂邊？<br />\n唔想再有呢啲事發生 唔想再比狗鄉黑恰<br />\n就由我地自己做野改變啦屌<br />\n講係無用架 要做呀"},{"pid":"4f3adf90fcf70ab3f8d74fdd4d6ef8ba4ada420d","tid":1373300,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"01c6642803ea588c9418b0f22ba9ddb834485a9e","tid":1373300,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"經過今晚，想問個legitimacy 夠未？"},{"pid":"8f0862fedaaf4b0a5542505ac2d8ddbb513c1b2e","tid":1373300,"uid":164374,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"請勇武要打狗既各自組隊打<br />\n唔好係連登公佈行動細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79174a766dfb7791b6f4a2a75e7dcfcf811ccd32","tid":1373300,"uid":197958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警為三萬蚊月薪<br />\n唔似義士為保家衛國<br />\n點會同你打<br />\n走都走唔切"},{"pid":"74e4a8a3fe2acd4b6e75a9d568ecbefe6598eda9","tid":1373300,"uid":110332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"係時候成立民間防衛隊做返警察應該做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n依家咁多證據都證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警察=黑社會</span></span>，依家嘅警察已經失去合法性<br />\n<br />\n首先可以由集體唔交稅開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7XMWCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7XMWCx.png&h=73fa9ee1&s={SIZE}\" />